Package com.flipfit.bean

Class Payment

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.Payment
public class Payment extends Object
The Payment class represents a payment transaction in the FlipFit system. It encapsulates details about a payment, including its unique ID, amount, date, and associated customer, gym, and slot IDs.

This class is a **Plain Old Java Object (POJO)** and is designed to hold data. It includes a default constructor and a parameterized constructor, along with standard getter and setter methods for all its fields.
